title: "ot-agent: Agentic OT asset classification and IEC 62443 control generation"
abstract: >
  Hybrid agentic pipeline for OT asset classification and IEC 62443 control
  generation. Combines a deterministic rules engine (ot-asset-classifier) with
  a local LLM fallback (Ollama/vLLM), three-tier control generation grounded
  in IEC 62443 standard text via ChromaDB RAG, a multi-turn chat interface,
  and a CSV/JSON batch pipeline. Designed for air-gapped operational technology
  environments with zero external network calls.
